::Repressor::

Repressor spins around as HotRod drives through the door, trasforming 
into vehicle mode and launching off at full speed. He could see the 
battle between Najah and the Maximal from a distance. He could also 
hear HotRod's boasts.

"We'll see about that, Maximal," he says quietly, more to himself 
than to HotRod, and fires two signature-seeking missiles at the bot.
